title: Modern Downtown Condo
description: Stunning modern condo in the heart of downtown with panoramic city views. This beautifully designed unit features an open floor plan, high-end finishes throughout, and floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the space with natural light. The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and custom cabinetry. The master suite includes a walk-in closet and spa-like bathroom with dual vanities and a soaking tub.

title: Charming Victorian Home
description: Beautifully restored Victorian home with original character and modern amenities. This charming property features original hardwood floors, decorative moldings, and period-appropriate fixtures. The updated kitchen includes modern appliances while maintaining the home's historic charm. Large front porch perfect for morning coffee, and a private backyard with mature landscaping.

title: Luxury Waterfront Penthouse
description: Spectacular penthouse with unobstructed ocean views and luxury finishes throughout. This stunning residence features floor-to-ceiling windows, marble floors, and a chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances. The master suite opens to a private terrace overlooking the bay. Building amenities include a rooftop pool, spa, and 24-hour concierge.

title: Cozy Studio Apartment
description: Bright and cozy studio apartment perfect for urban living. Features an efficient layout with tall ceilings and large windows. The modern kitchen includes all appliances, and the bathroom has been recently updated. Located in a vibrant neighborhood with easy access to public transportation, restaurants, and shopping.

title: Family Suburban Home
description: Spacious family home in a quiet neighborhood with excellent schools. This well-maintained property features an open floor plan, updated kitchen with granite countertops, and a large master suite with walk-in closet. The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a deck and mature trees. Two-car garage and plenty of storage throughout.

title: Industrial Loft Apartment
description: Unique industrial loft in a converted warehouse building. Features exposed brick walls, high ceilings with exposed beams, and large industrial windows. The open layout is perfect for creative living and includes polished concrete floors and modern fixtures. Located in the trendy warehouse district with galleries, restaurants, and nightlife.

title: Beachfront Cottage
description: Charming beachfront cottage with direct beach access and stunning ocean views. This cozy retreat features an open living area with vaulted ceilings, a stone fireplace, and sliding doors that open to a deck overlooking the Pacific. The property has been recently renovated while maintaining its coastal charm. Perfect for a weekend getaway or year-round living.

title: Modern Townhouse
description: Contemporary townhouse in a sought-after neighborhood near downtown Nashville. This three-level home features an open concept main floor with hardwood throughout, a gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, and a spacious master suite with walk-in closet. Private rooftop deck with city views. Attached garage and modern energy-efficient systems.

title: Luxury High-Rise Apartment
description: Luxurious apartment on the 45th floor with breathtaking city and lake views. This elegant unit features floor-to-ceiling windows, premium finishes, and a modern kitchen with high-end appliances. Building amenities include a fitness center, swimming pool, business center, and 24-hour doorman. Located in the heart of downtown with easy access to shopping, dining, and transportation.

title: Historic Brownstone
description: Meticulously maintained Victorian brownstone in Boston's prestigious Back Bay neighborhood. This elegant home features original architectural details including ornate moldings, medallions, and marble fireplaces. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with modern amenities while preserving historic character. Private garden and parking space included.

title: Mountain View Ranch
description: Stunning ranch-style home with panoramic mountain views on over an acre of land. Features vaulted ceilings, a stone fireplace, and large windows throughout that showcase the natural beauty. The gourmet kitchen opens to a great room perfect for entertaining. Master suite with private deck. Oversized three-car garage and workshop space.

title: Urban Duplex
description: Stylish duplex apartment in trendy Williamsburg with modern finishes and abundant natural light. The main floor features an open living and dining area with exposed brick accent wall. Upstairs loft bedroom with skylight and walk-in closet. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops. Private outdoor space and washer/dryer included.
